v1.0.0 (2025-01-08)
- Initial release
- Automatic rating updates for movies and TV shows
- Support for IMDb and Trakt as rating sources
- Weighted average calculation when multiple sources are enabled
- Configurable update interval (in days)
- Year-based filter for movies
- Air date filter for TV shows
- Built-in log viewer for rating updates
- Rate limiting for API calls
- Detailed logging system 